{"tid":1689834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警暴、裝修、梁振英貪污，有咩分別？","createTime":"2019-11-03T04:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T23:27:49.000Z","uid":74778,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"80588bec46e8e347c8f0a117766ca1fd1ebf8bd6","tid":1689834,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分別係警暴同梁振英貪污，喺破壞治安嘅同時，仲係以 權 謀 私！係破壞法治！<br />\n<br />\n黑警前線胡作非為，係破壞治安！<br />\n<strong>後勤高層瘋狂鳩嗡，兇政務司兇行政長官<span style=\"color: red;\">，為前線黑警脫罪，無得到應有懲罰，係破壞香港法治！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f3ElKlG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff3ElKlG.png&h=246d23e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://x7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/10/%E8%AC%9D%E6%8C%AF%E4%B8%AD-1024x577.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fx7n5x3t5.stackpathcdn.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F10%2F%25E8%25AC%259D%25E6%258C%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD-1024x577.jpg&h=b00d4914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/67522135_10161909235615265_3126601776191504384_o_Vz2P9_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F67522135_10161909235615265_3126601776191504384_o_Vz2P9_1200x0.png&h=0f2649cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/pk-22_p0grN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpk-22_p0grN_1200x0.png&h=eac96ab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcSQJBY_RQYJl90NRnErr-zQ0eu90tRV9iHPS3fO9RdiqawtxG0r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcSQJBY_RQYJl90NRnErr-zQ0eu90tRV9iHPS3fO9RdiqawtxG0r&h=dc1f97c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br /